(Recommended Fixes Before Planner Becomes Runtime Source of Truth) Tj
/F1 9.50 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 692.75 Tm
(1. Add an explicit day-type classifier that resolves one primary day type before block construction.) Tj
/F1 9.50 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 680.25 Tm
(2. Treat `core` as accessory/support work, not as a lift-defining category by itself.) Tj
/F1 9.50 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 667.75 Tm
(3. Treat `mobility` as mobility/support work, never as a lift-defining category.) Tj
/F1 9.50 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 655.25 Tm
(4. For `zone-2` workouts, classify run as primary and keep core/mobility supportive; do not create a) Tj
/F1 9.50 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 642.75 Tm
(   workout/lift logging target from core support.) Tj
/F1 9.50 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 630.25 Tm
