/F1 9.50 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 617.75 Tm
(   should be displayed separately from both run and lift.) Tj
/F1 9.50 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 605.25 Tm
(6. Keep Long Run Day protected: no lift block, no accidental hybrid, no extra conditioning beyond) Tj
/F1 9.50 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 592.75 Tm
(   prescribed long run.) Tj
/F1 9.50 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 580.25 Tm
